{
  "texts": [
    "Other methods and regulations are required to deter such attacks.",
    "We expect that e-commerce giants will not engage in deliberate attempts to violate local privacy laws because they have reputations to protect.",
    "However, individual DSPs may engage in such attacks.",
    "E-commerce giants can deter DSPs from engaging in such attacks by requiring the DSP to provide a live photograph of the drone prior to take-off from the warehouse, which can subsequently be examined for the presence of unauthorized attachments.",
    "Finally, several models of drones can either themselves record audio or carry peripherals to do so."
  ]
}